description: A compact 14-round 5.56 NATO magazine compatible with STANAG rifles, an alternative to the older Ruger 5.56x45mm mag, it is almost identical to its version for 5.56 Electrothermal.
A lightweight 24-round 5.56 NATO casket magazine compatible with STANAG rifles, almost identical to its version for 5.56 Electrothermal. Amazingly compact but less reliable and tricky to reload.
A lighter and more reliable STANAG standard capacity magazine proposed as a replacement for its predecessor of same shape and size, it is almost identical to its version for 5.56 Electrothermal.
A lighter and more reliable 50-round STANAG drum magazine proposed as replacement for its predecessor of same shape and size, it is almost identical to its version for 5.56 Electrothermal.
A lightweight 60-round 5.56 NATO casket magazine compatible with STANAG rifles, almost identical to its version for 5.56 Electrothermal. Amazingly compact but less reliable and tricky to reload.
A lightweight 100-round 5.56 NATO casket magazine compatible with STANAG rifles, almost identical to its version for 5.56 Electrothermal. Amazingly compact but less reliable and tricky to reload.
